text: Antoine Pierre Schildwein was a gymnast from France. Schildwein competed at the 1936 Summer Olympics and the 1948 Summer Olympics. He was born on 10 August 1911 and died on 24 September 1995.Antoine Schlindwein == References == Category:1911 births Category:1995 deaths Category:French gymnasts Category:Olympians for France Category:People from Moselle Category:Sportspeople from Grand Est
